column5: Hi folks I'm new here bin a lurker for a few months I'm mostly into Bird and Macro photography as of late Just got a Nikon D5100 and started birding in april I also like Macro photography I picked up a Tamron 90mm F2.8 lens for that any way love the fish stories hope to read lots more   Thanks Kevin
